<plot>Coed Sophie Hoffkind, in search of her sexual identity, spins into crisis after she sleeps with her professor and he unexpectedly dies the morning after. Out of her guilt and her compulsive need to make things right again, she betrays her boyfriend and bisexual girlfriend in order to pursue his widow in search of forgiveness. Sophie is lost in the power that sex seems to give her, and it isn't until she becomes stranded with the widow that she is confronted with the truth of her narcissistic behavior.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?043585</url></doc>
